name: NB:This line should contain a numeric for Matlab
stcConfId: id of the group of conf parameters to build raw, gap and stc cubes
snowCoverDayConfId: id of the group of conf params to build snow_cover_days variable
mosaicConfId: Id of the group of conf params to build daily Mosaics
statisticConfId: Id of the group of conf params to generate statistic files. Used only for big Regions, not used at the tile level.
publishConfId: Id of the group of conf params to generate geotiffs (historic and nrt web)
commentOnBigRegion: Big region the tile is historically associated with. For info only
id: Id indicated in toolsRegion.sh. NB: for region of type bigRegion, this id differs from the id of the group0 landsubdivision indicated in configuration_of_landsubdivisions.csv.
versionOfAncillary: Version of ancillary files, v3.1, v3.2, or test
historicStartWaterYear: Historic: understood as all historics, including the nrt jpl files from the last years
